### 9. Script de build pour la documentation

**`scripts/build_docs.sh`** :
```bash
#!/bin/bash

echo "ğŸ”¨ Building unified documentation..."

# Build Rust docs
echo "ğŸ“š Building Rust documentation..."
cargo doc --workspace --no-deps

# Build Python docs (si applicable)
echo "ğŸ Building Python documentation..."
cd python_lib
python -m pdoc --html --output-dir ../docs/api/python ftp_core_python

cd ..

# Build MkDocs site
echo "ğŸŒ Building MkDocs site..."
cd docs
mkdocs build

echo "âœ… Documentation built successfully!"
```